---
import LegalLayout from "../components/LegalLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../lib/site";
---

<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" effective="July 19, 2025">
  <h2>Data Controller</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>{site.legalName}</strong><br />
    {site.address.line1}<br />
    {site.address.line2}<br />
    United States<br />
    {site.email} · {site.phones.office} · {site.phones.cell}
  </p>
  <p>
    {site.legalName} is the data controller responsible for processing personal data
    collected through this website.
  </p>

  <h2>Scope</h2>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, protect, and retain
    personal data submitted through our website, particularly via our contact forms.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <h3>1. Personal Information</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Full name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Message content</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>2. Usage Data</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address, browser type and version, device information</li>
    <li>Pages visited and time spent, date and time of access, referring URLs</li>
    <li>Analytics information</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
  <p>We use cookies for website functionality, improving user experience, analyzing site traffic and performance, and saving user preferences.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Respond to inquiries and contact form submissions</li>
    <li>Provide customer support and information about our services</li>
    <li>Improve our website and services</li>
    <li>Analyze website usage and trends</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>We do not use your personal information for third-party marketing purposes.</strong></p>

  <h2>Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Consent:</strong> when you submit forms or contact us</li>
    <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> to improve our services and website</li>
    <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> to comply with applicable laws</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. <strong>We do not share or disclose consumer data or opt-in information to third parties for marketing or promotional purposes.</strong></p>
  <p>We may share information with service providers (hosting, IT, analytics under confidentiality agreements), as required by law, or to protect our rights, property, or safety.</p>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.</p>

  <h2>Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Restrict or object to certain processing</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.</p>

  <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>{site.legalName}</strong><br />
    {site.address.line1}, {site.address.line2}, USA<br />
    {site.email} · {site.phones.office} · {site.phones.cell}
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
